value.0: The quiet wood elf is usually seen with his ferret companion. As cleric and ranger of Solonor Thelandira he is an excellent archer and usually seen in the woods.
The calm and friendly moonelf Laf'aera is a cleric of Corellon and also has a talent as a bard. Her favorite instrument is the harp.
Shethal is a cleric and wizard of Labelas Enoreth. Often seen at the side or on the shoulder of the sun elf is her snow white owl familiar.
The stoic wild elf spends most of his time in the wilds with his fox companion. He is a devoted druid and priest of  Rillifane Rallathil.
